question.title: no suitable HttpMessageConverter found for response type [org.springframework.cloud.netflix.eureka.http.EurekaApplications]and contenttype [text/html]
question.body:
I am trying to deploy my application to AWS Fargate. I'm using Spring Boot version 3.1.2, JDK 17, Spring cloud 2022.0.2, spring-cloud-starter-netflix-eureka-server 4.0.1 version.

Eureka runs and UI is working fine. When I try to run my service it is giving me this error due to which it is not working. How can I fix it?
